tespace-pre!\">sfc /scannow  \ndism /online /cleanup-image /restorehealth\n</code></div></div></pre><p data-start=\"922\" data-end=\"1040\">Rebooted the computer afterward and asked the user to verify functionality &mdash; the system appeared to be working fine.</p><p data-start=\"1042\" data-end=\"1290\">Later, received another email from the user regarding <strong data-start=\"1096\" data-end=\"1131\">OneDrive synchronization issues</strong>. Reconnected to the system, ran <strong data-start=\"1164\" data-end=\"1182\">DISM utilities</strong> again, and rebooted. The <strong data-start=\"1208\" data-end=\"1228\">Office 365 suite</strong> was also repaired to ensure stable application performance. Again got a mail regarding the excel issue so tried to contact with her on remote chat as well as on mail so waiting for her response. </p></span></span>",
